reviewText: Yes, great series...looking for more similar series/ titles to purchase....

Bought this for in-laws. They have watched and found the series to be well done and very interesting. In fact they let some close friends borrow to watch and they also commented that the series was very good. I will have to buy others series for them in near future.
Great drama and glad I ordered it. Type of drama I will get in the future. The service was excellent.
